<table>
<tr><td colspan=2><u><b>Global Keyboard Shortcuts:</u></b></td></tr>
<tr><td>PAUSE (or SLEEP)</td><td>Lock Screen</td></tr>
<tr><td>SHIFT+PAUSE (or STOP)</td><td>Disconnect Session</td></tr>
